    def:Card_Text "Once during the game, when you use the ”Plough 1 Field” action space, you can plough 3 fields instead of 1." ;
    def:Prerequisite "1 Occupation" .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/U008>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/affects> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/each_round> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/bonusPoints> "1" ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/clay> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "U008" ;
    rdfs:label "Muddy Bog" ;
    def:Card_Text "Place 1 Clay each on the next 2 Round spaces. At the start of each round, you receive the Clay." ;
    def:Prerequisite "2 Occupations" .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/A2>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/affects> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/whenever> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/bonusPoints> "1" ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/bake>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/cooking>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/food> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/hasCost> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/3c> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "A2" ;
    rdfs:label "Fireplace" ;
    def:Card_Text "At any time, you may convert goods to food as follows: vegetable →2 food; sheep →2 food; wild boar →2 food; cattle →3 food. Whenever you use a bread baking action, you may convert: grain →2 food." .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/A9>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/affects> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/end_of_game>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/harvest> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/bonusPoints> "2" ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/bonus_points>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/food>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/reed> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/hasCost> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/2r2s> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "A9" ;
    rdfs:label "Basketmaker’s Workshop" ;
    def:Card_Text "In each harvest, you can use the Basketmaker’s Workshop to convert exactly 1 reed to 3 food. At the end of the game, you receive 1/2/3 bonus points for 2/4/5 reed." .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/FR040>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/affects> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/other_players> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/action_space>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/field>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/stone> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "FR040" ;
    rdfs:label "Park Cemetary" ;
    def:Card_Text "Place 3 Stone on the ”Plow 1 field” Action space from the general supply. Any player who uses that space may also receive 1 Stone from it. If there is no Stone on that space, you may discard this card and Plow 1 field." .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/FR045>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/bonusPoints> "1" ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/renovation> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/hasCost> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/1s> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "FR045" ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/relatedTo> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/Renovate> ;
    rdfs:label "Stone House Reconstruction" ;
    def:Card_Text "You can Renovate your Clay hut to a Stone house at any time without using the ”Renovate” action. (You must still pay for the Renovation.)" .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/G44502>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/affects> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/end_of_game>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/immediately>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/other_players> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/bonus_points>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/wood> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "G44502" ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/relatedTo> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/Fences> ;
    rdfs:label "Animal Husbandry Worker" ;
    def:Card_Text "If there are still 3/6/9 rounds to play, you may immediately take a ”Fences” action and pay 2/3/4 Wood less. At the end of the game, all players with the most pastures receive 2 Bonus points." .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/G45685>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/affects> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/each_round> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/wood> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "G45685" ;
    rdfs:label "Master Fencer" ;
    def:Card_Text "Once you live ina Send house, you may pay 2/3 Wood at the start of each round to build 3/4 fences." .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/G56015>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/affects> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/each_round> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/boar>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/cattle>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/clay>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/sheep>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/stone>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/wood> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "G56015" ;
    rdfs:label "Animal Tamer’s Apprentice" ;
    def:Card_Text "At the start of each round, you receive 1 Sheep/Wild boar/Cattle for each Wood/ Clay/Stone room in your home that is not occupied by a Family member." .

<http://veronahe.no/agricola/G56243>    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/gains> <http://veronahe.no/agricola/occupation>, <http://veronahe.no/agricola/stable> ;
    <http://veronahe.no/agricola/id> "G56243" ;
    rdfs:label "Engineering Apprentice" ;
    def:Card_Text "When you play your and, 3rd, sth, and 7th Occupation, you can build 1 stable at no cost afterward. (If you play this card as your 2nd, 3rd, sth, or 7th Occupation, build 1 stable at no cost afterward.)" .

